sequenceDiagram
    title Hybrid RAG - Cache Sequence Flow

    actor U as User/Browser
    participant WS as WS /ws/chat
    participant SR as _shared_retrieve_documents
    participant CB as LazyCache / CacheBackend
    participant R as HybridRetriever
    participant L2 as L2 Embedding LRU
    participant V as ChromaDB (persistent)

    U->>WS: send_json {query, enable_rerank}
    WS->>WS: validate query length and retriever readiness
    WS-->>U: send {type: "status"}
    WS->>WS: generate correlation_id and cache_status list
    WS->>SR: _shared_retrieve_documents(query, enable_rerank, ...)

    SR->>SR: normalize query
    SR->>SR: resolve effective_enable_rerank
    SR->>SR: build config_fingerprint (SHA-256)
    SR->>SR: build shared_identity + corpus_version
    SR->>SR: build cache_key = shared-retrieve:SHA-256(JSON)
    SR->>CB: lazy_cache.get(cache_key)

    Note over SR,CB: Cache HIT path
    CB-->>SR: cached results (list)
    SR->>SR: log retrieval_hit and append "HIT"
    SR-->>WS: return cached results
    WS->>WS: filter score >= 0.80
    WS-->>U: {type:"results", cache_status:"HIT"}

    Note over SR,CB: Cache MISS path
    CB-->>SR: None (miss or fail-open fallback)
    SR->>SR: append "MISS"
    SR->>R: retrieve(query, enable_rerank=effective_enable_rerank)

    R->>L2: _get_or_encode_embedding(query)
    L2->>L2: SHA-256 key lookup
    alt L2 hit
        L2-->>R: cached embedding
    else L2 miss
        R->>R: encode query via SentenceTransformer
        R->>L2: cache embedding
        L2-->>R: embedding
    end

    R->>V: collection.query(query_embeddings, semantic_top_k)
    V-->>R: semantic results
    R->>R: keyword search (stop-word filtered)
    R->>R: weighted score fusion
    opt rerank enabled and reranker available
        R->>R: cross-encoder rerank
    end
    R->>R: source deduplication
    R-->>SR: return results

    SR->>CB: lazy_cache.set(cache_key, results)
    SR-->>WS: return results
    WS->>WS: filter score >= 0.80
    WS-->>U: {type:"results", cache_status:"MISS"}